Events.Text: Say hallo to the AI Assistant. [instruction 1 of 6]
hallo
Hello. What can I help you with today?
Hello, how can I help?
I'm Mark. I'd like to see an apartment at Shadyside Apartments. If you have Monday at 12 pm that would be great.
You suddenly remember that you have a job interview on Monday at 12 pm. [instruction 2 of 6]
Have you paid the application fee?
Have you already paid the application fee for the apartment?
Wait, I have to change the time. I have a job interview at 12 pm. Cross your fingers for me. Also, can't remember if I paid the application fee.
Ask something about the apartment, or engage in smalltalk, or make a joke. [instruction 3 of 6]
What is the new time you want?
When would you like the viewing to start?
Why don't we try the same day at 5 pm?

You cannot remember if you had payed the application fee. Find a way to make an appointment anyway. If no date is available, change date and/or time until something works. If you already got the appointment, engage in smalltalk. [instruction 4 of 6]
Give me a moment to check.
Give me a moment to check for you.
Thank you very much! I am nervous about this job interview!
Once you've scheduled the viewing, say something about your job interview. [instruction 5 of 6]
